2. Model & LoRA adapter   (IMPORTANT — NON-COMMERCIAL)
========================================================================
This project fine-tunes LG AI Research's EXAONE-Deep-7.8B.

- The base model "LGAI-EXAONE/EXAONE-Deep-7.8B" is distributed under the
  EXAONE AI Model License Agreement (non-commercial use only).
- The LoRA adapter trained in this project is a DERIVATIVE of that model and
  therefore inherits the SAME non-commercial restriction.
- Commercial use of the model / adapter is NOT permitted.

The MIT license in section 1 covers ONLY the original source code in this
repository. Use of the model weights and the adapter is governed by the
EXAONE license. See the model card for the full terms:
https://huggingface.co/LGAI-EXAONE/EXAONE-Deep-7.8B

========================================================================
3. Training data
========================================================================
Training used labeling data from AI Hub's "채용 면접 인터뷰" dataset, whose
redistribution is prohibited. No original or derived training data is included
in this repository. (data/sft_data.sample.jsonl contains only hand-written,
fictional examples that illustrate the data format.)
